description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured Sundance, VPR cast members, and Stu Chains. Over on The Bachelorette, Tayshia did her hometown dates at the La Quinta Inn on an apparently shoestring production budget.


Bachelorette Recap: 25:58ish
